title: Advanced Photoshop: The Premium Collection Vol. 8
description:
The magazine for Adobe Photoshop professionals and enthusiasts
Advanced Photoshop is the perfect magazine for honing already great Photoshop skills.

Each issue is packed full of inspiring interviews and challenging tutorials, tailor-made for the more advanced digital artist. 

Whether you're a Photoshop professional or simply aspiring to be one, Advanced Photoshop will help you perfect your art.

Genre: Magazine
